@startuml
title G&G Revamp - YPS Service Component Diagram
left to right direction
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial

actor "G&G / Capital Sale Staff" as Staff
rectangle "POS Device\n<<external>>\nSunmi POS / YPS POS" as POS
rectangle "YPS Service\n<<external>>\nProcess YPS Top Up" as ExtYPS
rectangle "YPS File Server\n<<external>>" as FileServer
rectangle "G&G Backend\n<<external>>\nAccept for email processing" as Backend
rectangle "ERP System DB (AX/D365)\n<<external>>" as ERP

package "YPS Service Container" {

  component "Push Money API\n<<component>>\nAccept & Process YPS\nTransaction Data" as PushMoney
  component "Sale Publish Component\n<<component>>\nValidate bill, product, store\nand prepare sale payload" as Publish
  component "CSV Import Component\n<<component>>\nRead CSV from file server\nand import for sale process" as Import
  component "Scheduler Component\n<<component>>\nTrigger file import,\nretry, and shift-close flow" as Scheduler
  component "Notification Component\n<<component>>\nSend import fail mail\nand fail transaction records" as Email
  component "Shift Validation Component\n<<component>>\nCheck sale sync status\nand close shift after import" as ShiftCheck

  queue "RabbitMQ / Kafka\n<<messaging>>\nYPS raw sale queue" as MQ
  database "Redis Cache\n<<cache>>\nBill / Product / Store" as Redis
  database "G&G Database\n<<database>>\nReference Data:\nBill, Product, Store" as GGDB
  database "YPS Database\n<<database>>\nImportRecord, ImportSession,\nFileConfig, Outbox" as YPSDB
}

Staff --> POS : operate
POS --> ExtYPS : send transaction [HTTPS]
POS --> PushMoney : send bill data [HTTPS/API]

PushMoney --> Publish : send raw transaction
Publish --> Redis : read cache
Publish --> GGDB : fetch reference data [JDBC]
Publish --> MQ : publish sale data [AMQP]
Publish --> YPSDB : save YPS transaction / outbox [JDBC]

Scheduler --> Import : trigger file import (1:30 AM)
Import --> FileServer : fetch CSV file
Import --> YPSDB : save import record/session [JDBC]
Import --> Publish : push sale data
Import --> Email : send fail import data

Scheduler --> ShiftCheck : trigger end-of-shift validation
ShiftCheck --> YPSDB : find import record / update shift status
ShiftCheck --> GGDB : check sale sync status

Email --> Backend : send fail data [REST]

MQ --> ERP : consume / sync sale data

@enduml